  <p> In addition, TrueWinter may share data with trusted partners to help us perform statistical analysis, send you email or postal mail, provide customer support, arrange for deliveries, or otherwise help provide the service. All such third parties are prohibited from using your personal information except to provide these services to TrueWinter, and they are required to maintain the confidentiality of your information. TrueWinter does not use or disclose sensitive personal information, such as race, religion, or political affiliations, without your explicit consent.</p>
